-- Beijing Enterprises Water Completes Standard Water Project Deal
-- B y   B e i   H u
-- 2013-09-09T09:38:23Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-09-09/beijing-enterprises-water-completes-standard-water-project-deal.html
Beijing Enterprises Water Group Ltd. (371) 
completed the 1.35 billion-yuan ($220 million) acquisition of a
pair of Standard Water Ltd. subsidiaries involved in 36 water
projects in Shandong, Shanxi and elsewhere in China.  The water-treatment systems developer, which announced the
purchases in July, said in a  Hong Kong  stock exchange filing
yesterday that it also agreed to pay off almost 518 million yuan
in debt as terms of the deal to acquire the units Crystal Water
Co. and China Water Holdings Pte.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bei Hu in Hong Kong at 
